==Korean==
===Noun===
'''해마''' ([[海馬]], ''haema''), literally, "sea horse" 
#[[sea horse]] (''fish''), i.e., the genus [[Hippocampus]] 
#[[sea horse]] (''mammal''), i.e., [[walrus]]

===Etymology===
From hanja: [[海馬]], made up of [[海]], "sea" + [[馬]], "horse"

